(3269, 'en', 'plugindomain', '3a9d4d653f8f67d118c34cd4357b3948', 'The Avia Layout Builder allows you to create unique layouts with an easy to use, drag and drop interface.<br/><br/>The Builder is available on Pages and Single Portfolio Entries', NULL, 'LINE', NULL, 0, '', '85aa8fb803428acbd2eda447397a8941'),
(3270, 'en', 'default', '3ded626b75eebf44c0ca7a8587f84801', 'Creating a Page is very similar to creating a Post, and the screens can be customized in the same way using drag and drop, the Screen Options tab, and expanding/collapsing boxes as you choose. This screen also has the distraction-free writing space, available in both the Visual and Text modes via the Fullscreen buttons. The Page editor mostly works the same as the Post editor, but there are some Page-specific features in the Page Attributes box.', NULL, 'LINE', NULL, 0, '', '88d63d26a5d5ac5eef99a90931171ac9'),
