ref="https://wpml.org/documentation/plugins-compatibility/">Multilingual Ready Plugins</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Also, if you’re a theme or a plugin author and you want to make it compatible with WPML, we welcome you and ready to help: You are welcome to contact us at <a href="https://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/go-global-program/">go global program page</a>.</p>\n<p>In order to expedite the process, we strongly recommend that you test your theme or plugin with our <a href="https://wpml.org/documentation/support/achieving-wpml-compatibility-for-your-themes-and-plugins/">Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins</a>. It easily tests compatibility with WPML and helps you quickly make your theme or plugin Multilingual Ready.</p>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Miniblog</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Miniblog is responsive, minimal theme for bloggers.</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://themeforest.net/item/miniblog-multipurpose-minimal-wordpress-blog-theme/19284370" target="_blank">Purchase Miniblog</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Sumptuous</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Sumptuous is a multi-purpose WordPres theme</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://themeforest.net/item/sumptuous-creative-multipurpose-theme/4913367" target="_blank">Purchase Sumptuous</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">MF</h2>\n<blockquote><p>MF is a responsive, muti-purpose WordPress theme.</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://themeforest.net/item/mf-responsive-business-theme/18747445" target="_blank">Purchase MF</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Heap</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Personal Blogging Theme for WordPress.</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://themeforest.net/item/heap-a-snappy-responsive-wordpress-blog-theme/7422943" target="_blank">Purchase Heap</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Shopkeeper</h2>\n<blockquote><p>eCommerce WordPress theme</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://themeforest.net/item/shopkeeper-ecommerce-wp-theme-for-woocommerce/9553045" target="_blank">Purchase Shopkeeper</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=bIYKEwa_jGk:fLk8adqOQwI:D7DqB2pKExk"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=bIYKEwa_jGk:fLk8adqOQwI:D7DqB2pKExk" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=bIYKEwa_jGk:fLk8adqOQwI:gIN9vFwOqvQ"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=bIYKEwa_jGk:fLk8adqOQwI:gIN9vFwOqvQ" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=bIYKEwa_jGk:fLk8adqOQwI:V_sGLiPBpWU"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=bIYKEwa_jGk:fLk8adqOQwI:V_sGLiPBpWU" border="0"></img></a>\n</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/wpml/~4/bIYKEwa_jGk" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:57:"https://wpml.org/2017/03/compatible-themes-mar-2017/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:42:"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0";a:1:{s:8:"origLink";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:52:"https://wpml.org/2017/03/compatible-themes-mar-2017/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:42:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:6:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:54:"Events Calendar is WooCommerce Multilingual compatible";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:51:"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/wpml/~3/c3nA4ymMEro/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:88:"https://wpml.org/2017/03/events-calendar-is-woocommerce-multilingual-compatible/#respond";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Mon, 13 Mar 2017 14:58:52 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:13:"Compatibility";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:28:"https://wpml.org/?p=1228658/";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:375:"WooCommerce Multilingual and WPML now allow you to translate events, tickets, and other assets created using the popular Events Calendar plugin and its add-ons. The Events Calendar plugin offers many add-ons to for better handling of your events. You can now easily translate the following assets: Events Event Venues Event Organizers Event Tickets Event Categories [&#8230;]";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:5:"Dario";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:4819:"<p class="lead">WooCommerce Multilingual and WPML now allow you to translate events, tickets, and other assets created using the popular Events Calendar plugin and its add-ons.</p>\n<p>The <a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/the-events-calendar/">Events Calendar</a> plugin offers many add-ons to for better handling of your events. You can now easily translate the following assets:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Events</li>\n<li>Event Venues</li>\n<li>Event Organizers</li>\n<li>Event Tickets</li>\n<li>Event Categories and Tags</li>\n</ul>\n<p>All these features and assets can now be translated and used in multiple languages, thanks to the compatibility with WPML and WooCommerce Multilingual plugins.</p>\n<p>Please note that to translate assets created using the Events Calendar plugin and its add-ons, you need to use both WPML and <a href="https://wpml.org/documentation/related-projects/woocommerce-multilingual/">WooCommerce Multilingual</a>.</p>\n<div id="attachment_1228690" style="width: 310px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><a href="https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/events-calendar-woocommerce-multilingual-wpml-front-end-example.png"><img class="wp-image-1228690 size-medium" src="https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/events-calendar-woocommerce-multilingual-wpml-front-end-example-300x265.png" alt="A multilingual event featuring the language and currency switcher" width="300" height="265" srcset="https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/events-calendar-woocommerce-multilingual-wpml-front-end-example-300x265.png 300w, https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/events-calendar-woocommerce-multilingual-wpml-front-end-example-150x132.png 150w, https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/events-calendar-woocommerce-multilingual-wpml-front-end-example-768x678.png 768w, https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/events-calendar-woocommerce-multilingual-wpml-front-end-example-1024x904.png 1024w, https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/events-calendar-woocommerce-multilingual-wpml-front-end-example.png 1105w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">A multilingual event featuring the language and currency switcher</p></div>\n<p>Assets created using the <b>Events Calendar </b>and its add-ons are translated using the WPML’s Translation Editor, as shown in the following image.</p>\n<div id="attachment_1228691" style="width: 310px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><a href="https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/events-calendar-woocommerce-multilingual-translating-an-event.png"><img class="size-medium wp-image-1228691" src="https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/events-calendar-woocommerce-multilingual-translating-an-event-300x136.png" alt="Translating an event using WPML’s Translation Editor" width="300" height="136" srcset="https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/events-calendar-woocommerce-multilingual-translating-an-event-300x136.png 300w, https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/events-calendar-woocommerce-multilingual-translating-an-event-150x68.png 150w, https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/events-calendar-woocommerce-multilingual-translating-an-event-768x347.png 768w, https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/events-calendar-woocommerce-multilingual-translating-an-event-1024x463.png 1024w, https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/events-calendar-woocommerce-multilingual-translating-an-event.png 1264w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">Translating an event using WPML’s Translation Editor</p></div>\n<p>For complete description and instructions, visit our <a href="https://wpml.org/documentation/plugins-compatibility/using-event-calendar-with-woocoomerce-multilingual/">documentation page about using the Events Calendar plugin with WooCommerce Multilingual</a>.</p>\n<div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=c3nA4ymMEro:x3M_WaXFNAg:D7DqB2pKExk"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=c3nA4ymMEro:x3M_WaXFNAg:D7DqB2pKExk" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=c3nA4ymMEro:x3M_WaXFNAg:gIN9vFwOqvQ"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=c3nA4ymMEro:x3M_WaXFNAg:gIN9vFwOqvQ" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=c3nA4ymMEro:x3M_WaXFNAg:V_sGLiPBpWU"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=c3nA4ymMEro:x3M_WaXFNAg:V_sGLiPBpWU" border="0"></img></a>\n</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/wpml/~4/c3nA4ymMEro" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:85:"https://wpml.org/2017/03/events-calendar-is-woocommerce-multilingual-compatible/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:42:"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0";a:1:{s:8:"origLink";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:80:"https://wpml.org/2017/03/events-calendar-is-woocommerce-multilingual-compatible/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:42:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:1